rows.label: qev091502_MSG0004
rows.name: Frye and his team have breached Bedrock Hold.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091502_MSG0005
rows.name:
We succeeded in catching the Ganglion off guard,
and their ranks are a mess.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091502_MSG0006
rows.name:
They haven't managed much of a counteroffensive,
which is good news for us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091502_MSG0007
rows.name:
However, the other force we were worried about
is already on the move.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091502_MSG0009
rows.name:
Your job is to make them regret that.
Show them that the Ganglion are outmatched here![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev091502_MSG0013
rows.name: An unidentified hostile?! Give me a status report, now![ST:wait ]
